386→                        <div id="content">Let $A$ be a finite set of integers. Is it true that for every $\epsilon&#62;0$\[\max( \lvert A+A\rvert,\lvert AA\rvert)\gg_\epsilon \lvert A\rvert^{2-\epsilon}?\]</div>
